hwMeta.bodyText:
If(clk._onRisingEdge(),
    If(rst_n._eq(0),
        wr_ptr(0),
        size_reg(0),
        rd_ptr(0),
        looped(0)
    ).Else(
        wr_ptr(wr_ptr_next),
        size_reg(size_reg_next),
        rd_ptr(rd_ptr_next),
        looped(looped_next)
    )
)

If(st._eq(st_t.waitOnInput) & (sig_buff_size._eq(16) | timeoutCntr._eq(0)),
    wDatapump_req_vld(1),
    If(wDatapump_req_rd._eq(1),
        If(remaining - 1 < buffSize_tmp,
            offset_next(0),
            remaining_next(512)
        ).Else(
            offset_next(offset + Concat(Bits(5).from_py(0), sig_buff_size._reinterpret_cast(Bits(5)))._reinterpret_cast(Bits(10, signed=False))),
            remaining_next(remaining - Concat(Bits(5).from_py(0), sig_buff_size._reinterpret_cast(Bits(5)))._reinterpret_cast(Bits(10, signed=False)))
        ),
        sizeOfItems_next(sizeTmp._reinterpret_cast(Bits(5))),
        timeoutCntr_next(1023)
    ).Else(
        offset_next(offset),
        remaining_next(remaining),
        sizeOfItems_next(sizeOfItems),
        timeoutCntr_next(timeoutCntr)
    )
).Else(
    wDatapump_req_vld(0),
    If(sig_buff_dataOut_vld._eq(1) & st._eq(st_t.waitOnInput) & (timeoutCntr != 0),
        timeoutCntr_next(timeoutCntr - 1)
    ).Else(
        timeoutCntr_next(timeoutCntr)
    ),
    offset_next(offset),
    remaining_next(remaining),
    sizeOfItems_next(sizeOfItems)
)

If(clk._onRisingEdge(),
    If(rst_n._eq(0),
        uploadedCntr(0),
        timeoutCntr(1023),
        st(st_t.waitOnInput),
        remaining(512),
        offset(0),
        lastWordCntr(0)
    ).Else(
        uploadedCntr(uploadedCntr_next),
        timeoutCntr(timeoutCntr_next),
        st(st_next),
        remaining(remaining_next),
        offset(offset_next),
        lastWordCntr(lastWordCntr_next)
    )
)
